net.rtccloud.sdk

Interface MeetingPoint.Editor

  • Enclosing interface:
    MeetingPoint

    public static interface MeetingPoint.Editor
    Interface used for modifying values in a MeetingPoint object.
    All changes you make in an editor are batched, and not copied back to the original MeetingPoint until you call apply().

      • apply

        void apply()
        Asynchronous call
        Commit your changes back from this Editor to the MeetingPoint object it is editing.

        A StatusEvent with StatusEvent.getType() equals to StatusEvent.Type.UPDATED will be fired when the modifications are effective.
